{"tid":40100,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【李華華搶先睇】大戶4,500萬摸頂價買「越棧」 五日輸二千萬","createTime":"2016-12-15T03:47:09.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-15T09:04:50.000Z","uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4bcd5462041a3ba461dfe3fa315f6407b2b89c4b","tid":40100,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T03:47:09.000Z","msg":"爆升暴跌嘅「越南河粉股」膳源(1632)竟然有真心捧場客。 <br />\n<br />\n根據聯交所資料，有位叫做林均恆嘅仁兄，上周四，接近摸頂，以平均價16.6元，增持膳源270.4萬股，涉及資金約4,500萬元。 <br />\n<br />\n可惜，膳源最高見過17.5元之後就喪跌，今日收報8.2元，換言之，林均恆增持呢批貨，五日內賬面蝕2,270萬元。 <br />\n<br />\n林均恆因為增持膳源去到5%，達到披露水平，所以要開晒名畀大家知道佢摸頂掃入膳源。睇嚟佢真係好鍾意越南河囉。 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff166bd0dd170517ab807a8cac9d4bed1d96cef5","tid":40100,"uid":39133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T05:13:22.000Z","msg":"高登手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eae7f38a6b925f87fd5796f6c1fea7f5c9f7fa22","tid":40100,"uid":56511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T05:22:06.000Z","msg":"好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c9c3f1274c540fb0857a01362602502ab8447a6","tid":40100,"uid":3206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T05:25:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5676ba2ed50e10a25d55e7b94fb240b5ee2c26a","tid":40100,"uid":20524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T07:38:46.000Z","msg":"睇人仆街最開心系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84a775092eff5cdca6f41a30f7466efbb747f196","tid":40100,"uid":51673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T08:16:17.000Z","msg":"睇真d<br